s=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//5</span>\n Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">WriteLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sb1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Capacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n sb1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">Append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"12345678\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//12（自动扩容）</span>\n Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">WriteLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sb1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//123412345678</span>\n Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">WriteLine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sb1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Capacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//容量</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>二、StringBuilder和string的区别<br/> a.<br/> StringBuilder是字符串变量<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\6223d3b832d647f69346acffb9aaa441.png\"/><br/> string 是字符串常量<br/> b.<br/> string类型在进行运算的时候是重新生成了一个新的string对象，不适合大量频繁字符串的拼接或删除<br/> StringBuilder进行运算时，是一直在已有对象操作的，适合大量频繁字符串的拼接或删除</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}